description:
As of August 14 (2020) Vietnamese government states that Health declaration is mandatory for all passengers entering Vietnam, and recommends that all persons who have entered Vietnam from March 1 until the present should: 
1) Complete the medical declaration form here; 
2) Implement 14-day self-quarantine at home and limit contact with others after the 14-day period; 
3) Wear face masks, wash hands with soap or antiseptic alcohol, and take other preventive measures; 
4) Contact the nearest health facility for advice and support.
